---
const trustedList = [
  {
    link: "/home/hrf.webp",
  },

  {
    link: "/home/btrust.webp",
  },
];

const colabList = [
  {
    link: "/home/bob.webp",
  },
  {
    link: "/home/pts.webp",
  },
  {
    link: "/home/sob.webp",
  },
];
---

<div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl text-center lg:p-8">
  <h1
    class="my-8 font-header text-2xl font-bold md:text-3xl lg:text-6xl"
    id="about_us"
  >
    “So, what is it that you folks do at Bitshala?”
  </h1>

  <p class="text-basemd:text-lg m-4 lg:text-2xl">
    Bitshala is a <span class="font-bold text-orange"
      >grassroots education initiative</span
    > led by Indian Bitcoiners, focused on strengthening the
    Bitcoin ecosystem by <span class="font-bold text-orange"
      >nurturing and supporting Bitcoin FOSS (Free and Open
      Source Software) Devs</span
    >. Our mission is to equip people with the skills and
    knowledge needed to contribute to Bitcoin FOSS projects.
  </p>

  <div
    class="m-5 flex rounded-3xl border-2 border-black border-opacity-5 bg-peach lg:m-0 lg:mb-8 lg:mt-32"
  >
    <h1
      class="my-3 font-header text-base font-bold lg:my-8 lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-3 lg:text-3xl"
    >
      Trusted and Supported by
    </h1>
    <div
      class="flex items-center justify-end gap-6 pr-5 lg:w-[120%] lg:gap-10"
    >
      {
        trustedList.map((li) => (
          <a href={li.link}>
            <img
              src={li.link}
              class="h-8 object-contain lg:h-16"
              alt="Bitshala Logo"
            />
          </a>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="m-5 flex rounded-3xl border-2 border-black border-opacity-5 bg-peach lg:m-0 lg:mb-32"
  >
    <h1
      class="my-3 text-start font-header text-base font-bold lg:my-8 lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-3 lg:text-3xl"
    >
      In collaboration with
    </h1>
    <div
      class="flex items-center justify-end gap-6 pr-5 lg:w-[120%] lg:gap-10"
    >
      {
        colabList.map((li) => (
          <a href={li.link}>
            <img
              src={li.link}
              class="h-8 object-contain lg:h-16"
              alt="Bitshala Logo"
            />
          </a>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="m-4 text-base md:text-lg lg:text-2xl">
    We want you to be part of the revolution.
  </p>

